    "본문HTML": "<p>\n\n</p><p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 17pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">2026-1학기 Language Exchange Program 참가자 모집</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; word-break: keep-all;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; word-break: keep-all;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">2026학년도 1학기 본교 외국인 교환학생과 연계한 Language Exchange Program</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">(언어교환 프로그램) 참가자를 다음과 같이 모집하오니, </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">외국어 학습 및 교환학생과의 교류에 관심있는 재학생 여러분의 많은 신청 바랍니다 </span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; word-break: keep-all;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; word-break: keep-all;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">1. 시행 목적</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">가. 재학생의 외국어 능력 향상</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">나. 외국인 교환학생과 재학생 간 언어 및 문화교류 활성화</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">2. 운영 개요</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">가. 운영기간 : 2026-1</span>학기 (2026.4월~6월 (약 8주간))</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 10.4pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">나</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">. </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">외국인 교환학생(1~2명)</span>과 재학생(3</span>명 내외)이 스터디 그룹을 조직하여, 해당 외국어와 한국<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">어 상호 학습</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 10.4pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">    *외국인 학생으로부터 일방적으로 외국어를 배우는 것이 아님</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">다. 학습 외국어 : 영어, </span>중국어, 일본어, 프랑스어, 스페인어, 독일어(복수 외국어 신청불가)</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">라. <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">운영 그룹 수는 교환학생 및 재학생 수요에 따라 결정</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">3. 운영 방법</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 10.4pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">가</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">. </span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: -0.3pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">어학 수준 별 회화반 또는 어학시험(TOEIC, HSK, JLPT, TOPIK 등) </span>대비반 등 운영</span></span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">나. 학습방법 및 수업횟수 등은 각 그룹 내 협의를 통해 자율적으로 결정</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">다. 별도의 참가비 및 활동비 지급은 없음</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">라. 프로그램 종료 후 결과보고서 제출(참가자 확정 후 </span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">별도 안내 예정)</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\"> 및 우수 활동그룹 시상(기념품 제공)</span></span></p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 11pt;'> </p>\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 21pt; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all;'><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">4. 추진 일정</span></span></p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;'>\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 132px; border-top: 1pt solid black; border-right: 1pt solid black; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; border-image: initial; border-left: none; height: 21px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">내 용</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 255px; border-top: 1pt solid black; border-right: 1pt solid black; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; border-image: initial; border-left: none; height: 21px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all