one; border-image: initial; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; height: 32px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">이메일 접수</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 132px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; border-right: 1pt solid black; height: 21px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">신청서 심사</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">및 그룹매칭</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 255px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; border-right: 1pt solid black; height: 21px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">3.30.(월) ~ 4.1.(수)</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 214px; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-left: none; border-image: initial; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; height: 21px; text-align: center;\"> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 132px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; border-right: 1pt solid black; height: 21px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">참가대상자<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n\t\t\t확정 및 통보</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 255px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; border-right: 1pt solid black; height: 21px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">4.2.(목) </span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.5pt 5.25pt; width: 214px; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-left: none; border-image: initial; border-bottom: 1pt solid black; height: 21px;\">\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; text-indent: 11pt; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: keep-all; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: arial;\">이메일 통보</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box; height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 1.